title: Google ordered to pay $339m in damages following Chromecast ruling

title: Santa Barbara News-Press, one of California's oldest newspapers, folds after owner declares bankruptcy
text: SAN FRANCISCO — The Pulitzer Prize-winning Santa Barbara News-Press, one of California's oldest newspapers, has ceased publishing after its owner declared the 150-year-old publication bankrupt.
